title: Mary Higgins Clark E-Book Collection
description: Mary Theresa Eleanor Higgins Clark Conheeney ( born December 24, 1929[1]), known professionally as Mary Higgins Clark, is an American author of suspense novels. Each of her 42 books has been a bestseller in the United States and various European countries, and all of her novels remained in print as of 2007, with her debut suspense novel, Where Are The Children, in its seventy-fifth printing. Her suspense novels are very popular, and as of 2007 her books had sold more than 80 million copies in the United States alone.
